flavor_text_entries.gold:
Volcanoes erupt
when it barks. Un­
able to restrain its extreme power,
it races headlong
around the land.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
A POKéMON that
races across the
land. It is said that one is born
every time a new
volcano appears.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
This brawny
POKéMON courses
around the earth, spouting flames
hotter than a
volcano's magma.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
ENTEI embodies the passion of magma.
This POKéMON is thought to have been
born in the eruption of a volcano. It sends up massive bursts of fire that
utterly consume all that they touch.
